**base.html**
```html
[...]
&lt;body&gt;
    {% block header %}
        base header content
    {% endblock %}
    [...]
&lt;/body&gt;
```

**extended.html**
```html
{% extends &quot;base.html&quot; %}
{% block header %}
    {{ block.super }}
    new content added
{% endblock %}
